snippet.title: Fire Starter
snippet.description: Just when she thought she was out, they pull her back in; in ''The Hunger Games: Catching Fire,'' Katniss returns for an all-star fight to the death -- and transforms into a revolutionary; here's an inside look at the most anticipated movie of the fall

snippet.title: Star Treatment
snippet.description: Dalton investigates why ''Star Wars'' guru George Lucas has yet to take his rightful place on the Hollywood Walk of Fame. Plus: admiring Don Cheadle, and more notes on ''Viva Laughlin''
